{"tid":768426,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【盧凱彤墮斃】女歌迷到場獻鮮花︰感謝Ellen拍片鼓勵 走出人生低谷","createTime":"2018-08-05T11:28:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-06T05:15:57.000Z","uid":18213,"like":20,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ff536ed2385eca242f706bcbf53fb09bbc9f0bb8","tid":768426,"uid":18213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T11:28:45.000Z","msg":"女歌手盧凱彤（Ellen）今晨被發現在跑馬地寓所墮樓身亡，消息震驚港台樂壇。有歌迷得悉偶像死訊，下午帶同鮮花到場致哀。<br />\n<br />\n下午4時許，自稱是Ellen歌迷的楊小姐，與兩名友人帶同一束鮮花，打算到Ellen墮樓位置拜祭，惟大廈保安拒絕讓3人進入大廈。楊小姐向記者表示，中三開始聽at17的歌，今日得知Ellen的死訊，特意前來獻花，她本想將鮮花擺放大廈外，但保安員告知沒有人會接收後，即失望離去。未幾，楊小姐又再折返，並成功將鮮花交予保安員，轉交Ellen的家屬。<br />\n今年23歲的楊小姐表示，鍾意at17已5-6年，形容Ellen對她來說是一位十分重要的人，「佢係重要嘅支持者，支撐住我」。她透露當年考DSE時，墮入人生的低谷，友人找到Ellen拍了一輯短片替她加油打氣，後來她獲悉Ellen當時已患有抑鬱症，但仍然願意拍片鼓勵，她深受感動。楊小姐哽咽表示，會尊重Ellen的決定，「最緊要佢開心」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180805/58526674\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180805%2F58526674&d=rJonw%2FOR30HaaENIyD0zgpUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=b3d1f94d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180805%2F58526674&h=bfb90c9e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180805/58526674</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180805/large/1533458752_8bb3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180805%2Flarge%2F1533458752_8bb3.jpg&h=60d8fc60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180805/large/1533464475_fbd3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180805%2Flarge%2F1533464475_fbd3.jpg&h=40d25308&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n楊小姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8414aea97f58